 possible electronic states of $\\mathrm{OsBr_2}$, and confirm\nthat strong SOC combined with electronic correlation can induce multiple\nquantum phase transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 08:14:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-11"}
