olid state physics perspective where it is common and is\nassociated with point defects (metric anomalies) of the crystalline structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 14:13:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Apr 2022 14:37:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 01:09:08 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2022 14:36:23 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 19 Nov 2022 18:29:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
