t coherent curvature radiation as a\npromising candidate for pulsar radio emission mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 14:41:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 12:22:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-16"}
